{"tid":1476442,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] 警元朗檢7汽油彈　拘三人包括兩內地男","createTime":"2019-08-15T22:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T22:49:48.000Z","uid":224066,"like":162,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"c01e303ebd9d9bc309b205b67db276f0bc014eb1","tid":1476442,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T22:08:32.000Z","msg":"警方今早在巡邏期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">發現一輛私家車停泊在元朗青山公路屏山段往天水圍方向路邊</span>，形迹可疑，遂上前截查。3名站在私家車旁的男子隨即往元朗方向逃去，另一名男子則駕駛私家車向屯門方向逃去，警員隨即上前追截。另一批警員在一個由私家車掉落的紙箱內，檢獲7個懷疑氣油彈。3名逃跑的男子涉嫌藏有工具可作非法用途被捕，包括一名35歲李姓內地男子、61歲程姓男子及26歲李姓內地男子。案件交由元朗警區刑事調查隊第十二隊跟進，並正追緝駕車離開的男子。35歲李姓內地男子逃走期間意外受傷，報稱手痛，清醒被送博愛醫院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%85%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%25AA%25A27%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7&d=veK8Cd5y3rx0%2F3TK36JPEhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=00857241\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190815%2Fs00001%2F1565881331334%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%25AA%25A27%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588-%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25B7&h=8ad472cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190815/s00001/1565881331334/%E8%AD%A6%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%AA%A27%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88-%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%89%E4%B